# 1Ô∏è‚É£8Ô∏è‚É£ GOVERNANCE SAFEGUARDS

Risk forecasting must:

* Be auditable (Logic 14)
* Avoid discrimination bias
* Use transparent weighting
* Allow human override with justification
* Avoid automatic exclusion without review

It supports decisions ‚Äî it does not replace judgment.

